**CoinCard** is an exchange where bitcoins can be sold with payment received through [[PayPal]] or from a virtual prepaid debit card (gift card).

Payment is delivered nearly instantly after payment has [[confirmed|confirmation]].  CoinCard uses 2 blocks as the confirmation threshold.

The site was first publicly available on Feburary 25, 2011 (1.1). 

The operator of the site also operates [[CoinPal]] for [[buying_bitcoins]].

##Fees

* PayPal: Amounts under $50, 3%.  Amounts $50 and over, $1 plus 1%.
* Domino's Gift Card: 1%

